# ============================================================================
#  SAFETY GITIGNORE — blocks proprietary firmware, binaries, secrets, and
#  large files from EVER being committed to this public repo.
#  Docs + curated TEXT evidence only. If you must add a binary, force it
#  explicitly with `git add -f` after you are sure it is safe to publish.
# ============================================================================

# --- Proprietary / signed firmware (NEVER publish — copyright + legal) ---
*.img
*.bin
*.elf
*.melf
*.mbn
*.fv
*.pack
*.7z
*.zip
*.tar
*.tar.*
*.gz
*.xz
*.lz4
*.apk
*.dex
*.so
*.ko
*.dtb
*.dtbo
NON-HLOS*
BTFM*
dspso*
ODIN3_FOLDERS/
**/donor_downloads/
**/donor_extract*/
**/*firehose*
**/*prog_firehose*
**/xbl*
**/abl*
**/tz.*
**/keymint*
**/featenabler.mbn

# --- Raw disk / partition dumps ---
*.raw
*.sparse
*.roundtrip*
super_*.img
vendor_dlkm*.img
vbmeta*.img
boot*.img
metadata_*.img
userdata_*.img
persist.img

# --- Secrets / keys / credentials ---
*.pem
*.key
*.pk8
*.p12
*.keystore
*.jks
*.crt
*.cer
*.der
id_rsa*
*secret*
*token*
*.env
.env*

# --- Large files guard (manual review required to add anything big) ---
# (CI / pre-commit can enforce a hard size cap; see CONTRIBUTING.)

# --- OS / editor cruft ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*~
.idea/
.vscode/
node_modules/
site/            # mkdocs build output
.cache/

# --- Allow: documentation + curated text evidence ---
!**/*.md
!**/*.txt
!**/*.json
!**/*.log
!**/*.csv
!**/*.yml
!**/*.yaml
!docs/assets/*.svg
!docs/assets/*.png
